{"tid":1556763,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"太古城三百人合唱《願榮光歸香港》","createTime":"2019-09-10T00:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T00:59:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81c3c4149e5919e38ee08d71aafe0ce7d3138d64","tid":1556763,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:41:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190910/20765560\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F20765560&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=9d766fcb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190910%2F20765560&h=1178fcd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190910/20765560</a><br />\n<br />\n太古城三百人合唱《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190910/large/1568047278_07a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190910%2Flarge%2F1568047278_07a7.jpg&h=60becde5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約300名市民昨晚在太古城中心聚集，高叫口號及合唱《願榮光歸香港》。鄭大康攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港人日程停不了，約300名市民昨晚在港島太古城中心聚集，合唱《願榮光歸香港》，並高叫「光復香港，時代革命」等口號。現場有保安戒備，但秩序良好，人群其後和平散去。<br />\n<br />\n昨晚9時許，陸續有市民響應網上號召到太古城中心聚集。至10時原定活動開始時間，場內聚集市民越來越多，高峯期多達約300名市民，當中以年輕人較多，但亦不乏銀髮族，有母親更帶同嬰兒到場支持；不少人身穿黑衫，亦有人戴上黑色口罩。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：政界：或代表北京懷柔聲音<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n秩序良好 和平散去<br />\n<br />\n聚集市民主要分佈在太古城中心商場二至四樓，他們在玻璃圍欄前一字排開。活動期間，在場市民亮起手機電筒一同高呼「光復香港，時代革命」、「五大訴求，缺一不可」等口號。當這邊廂有人高喊：「香港警察」，那邊廂則有人和應：「吞槍自殺」。在場市民並多次合唱《願榮光歸香港》，一時間群情高漲。商場保安一直在場戒備，但未有干擾活動，活動至晚上約10時45分結束，其間秩序良好，之後人群和平散去。<br />\n<br />\n早前港鐵太古城站曾發生防暴警察及速龍小隊衝入站內，在扶手電梯追打市民，並近距離向示威者發射胡椒彈事件，其間險釀成人踩人。事件引起居民不滿，及後大批居民多次湧到站內抗議，並包圍車站控制室要求交代事件，譴責警方濫捕並使用過份武力。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄭大康 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n警家屬涉掟天仁茗茶襲警<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n警封路尋子彈<br />\n<br />\n政界：或代表北京懷柔聲音<br />\n138校人鏈高呼五大訴求<br />\n大學生接力築「城浸之路」<br />\n同學轟警不人道 撐重傷柏雨生<br />\n總警司：逃跑就要用棍毆<br />\n刀手傷女教師 石屎空襲人鏈<br />\n兆基學生斥何君堯自取其辱<br />\n羅范亂傳少女讓勇士洩慾<br />\n建制輿論大敗 製假新聞撐士氣<br />\n中大印度教授：港變警察國家<br />\n黃之鋒准離境 下周赴美國演講<br />\n警闖富雅搜捕刑毀 議員促賠償<br />\n萬人求美懲港官 北京惱羞成怒<br />\n亂襲記者 警：拉開零距離<br />\n3日拘157人 插贓疑團未解<br />\n無視律師信 取爆眼少女醫療報告<br />\n旺角藍衣人持利器襲示威者<br />\n民間記招譴責警腰斬25萬人集會<br />\n市民申索8.31太子站CCTV<br />\n被捕抗爭者控訴警膝壓頭 揑下體<br />\n孖仔涉毀輕鐵 維修費須28萬<br />\n林鄭巡站只關心閘機<br />\n英華校友籲港鐵高層勿忘校訓<br />\n警家屬涉掟天仁茗茶襲警<br />\n警封路尋子彈<br />\n李嘉誠籲執政者對青年網開一面"},{"pid":"f98767941db7836f7fc599771d3fc10d2634a459","tid":1556763,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:41:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acba83d87fd54eb3c092ca89ebe9d03fafb3e8c2","tid":1556763,"uid":20723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0pEqbc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0pEqbc4.png&h=1f16fd8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=0ae54964\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-communist-china-government-redeem-imperial-dynasty-s-bond</a><br />\n<br />\n任何國際之間既債務都有繼承義務<br />\n慈禧簽果條辛丑條約 一戰果時民國繼續還<br />\n仲要還到1938年因爲打二戰窮到pk<br />\n去求條約國唔追辛丑賠款先可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpU2AG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjpU2AG.jpg&h=45a46f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Yes! US</span></strong></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4278a1e76461ee83674f1ffaed713bbd08f4a5a3","tid":1556763,"uid":44028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我愛太古"},{"pid":"b8fdedcf3fb312850a1cc9e4ab6460b0c652079c","tid":1556763,"uid":258731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T00:52:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a14NDGA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa14NDGA.png&h=b89ad2c6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KL7GH8h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKL7GH8h.png&h=85dd15fd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HEYe28i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHEYe28i.png&h=4c7ba601&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aw6Xgt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faw6Xgt9.jpg&h=be74ca58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提撚晒水<br />\n大家識做啦<br />\n搞親共商家嘅威力會比圍狗屋大好多倍<br />\n<br />\n因為我哋係用行動方式直接懲罰啲出賣香港人長遠利益嘅機構<br />\n要佢哋知道我哋香港人唔係好蝦！😡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" clas